{"tid":1230302,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"眼淚真係忍唔住","createTime":"2019-06-16T07:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T09:18:16.000Z","uid":73024,"like":57,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"96f94813c9c01b0eb855b839a69600286acfd499","tid":1230302,"uid":73024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:08:18.000Z","msg":"尋晚件事情緒一直失控，喊左好多次。<br />\n本身以為柒婆話暫緩，好多人今日都唔會出黎。<br />\n今日一出街見到成條街都係黑衫人。<br />\n一d政治冷感既朋友都打俾我問我係邊度等，一齊出發。<br />\n本身諗住今日自己行既我，係巴士上面望住身邊既同路人，眼淚係咁湧出黎。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">感謝身邊每位香港人</span></span>"},{"pid":"382708c1b2e83d2b736fe0b337798d8d5d494c27","tid":1230302,"uid":121291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:09:02.000Z","msg":"共勉之，香港人加油！"},{"pid":"6324d3cb05ee20a943c96ae110e1a18dd4d80aa5","tid":1230302,"uid":167648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:09:53.000Z","msg":"我12/6果日都喊左<br />\n我好少喊 仲要係條街度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"837deef78eacf142d12331b27b603995eedb76e7","tid":1230302,"uid":229955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:10:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y9hCJKF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY9hCJKF.jpg&h=0756c303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大會宣布 提前出發 @ 14:30 <br />\n<br />\n1) 由維園 去 金鐘添美道<br />\n2) 2 條 BANNER : 「痛心疾首」 「撤回惡法」 由宗教界 同 一班媽媽帶領<br />\n3) 「痛心疾首」 BANNER 會放喺適當地方 , 畀各市民獻花<br />\n4) 有宗教界負責安排 祈禱會<br />\n5) 有支援抗爭者基金籌款箱<br />\n<br />\n616 黑色大遊行 五大宗旨:<br />\n<br />\n1) 撒回惡法<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><br />\n2) 釋放被捕既抗爭者<br />\n3) 我們不是暴徒<br />\n4) 追究黑警開槍責任<br />\n5) 淋病下台</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警冷血，林鄭殺港<br />\n無線新聞，出賣港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人加油</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d871f04170866d356bdec105e477ea65cfb84a","tid":1230302,"uid":49918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:13:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c6e6ed6d040e6973bb8bc542643cadab944b939","tid":1230302,"uid":73024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"15d871f04170866d356bdec105e477ea65cfb84a","tid":1230302,"uid":49918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:13:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:15:31.000Z","msg":"每次見到鄺神張相就好心up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db422bd94d0f732771751a8ce833efa20f2a897","tid":1230302,"uid":73024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf01e0369da64aac65014182c4cf5b83705be4a","tid":1230302,"uid":73024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff96b96a09eddd4ba1cc6c4d095dc60bbb92f92b","tid":1230302,"uid":126005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T09:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}